OL,3,C'It's ok to be bold': Women encouraged
OL,4,Cto build businesses
OL,6,FAround 160 business women have
OL,7,Fgathered to celebrate their
OL,8,Fachievements as entrepreneurs.
OL,10,FIn the South of Scotland, 52 percent
OL,11,Fof the population are women. The event
OL,12,Fin Gretna Green brought those in the
OL,13,Fbusiness world together, ahead of
OL,14,FInternational Women's Day.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
