OL,3,C'It's ok to be bold': Women encouraged
OL,4,Cto build businesses
OL,6,FIt was hosted by South of Scotland
OL,7,FEnterprise. The Chief Executive, Jane
OL,8,FMorrison-Ross said: "There's a
OL,9,Fsignificant number of start ups that
OL,10,Fare female-led. But I think things
OL,11,Flike today's event are part of that
OL,12,Fdrive."
OL,14,FSusan Harkin, head of innovation and
OL,15,Fentrepreneurship said: "You need to be
OL,16,Fvisible. It helps future generations
OL,17,Fof women to know they can do it.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
