CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1772745127
OL,3,C'It's ok to be bold': Women encouraged
OL,4,Cto build businesses
OL,6,F"But it makes good economic sense.
OL,7,FWomen are good at business, they are
OL,8,F52 percent of the population.
OL,9,FEconomically if we have more women
OL,10,Fstarting up in business, it makes a
OL,11,Fmuch wealthier, equal economy."
OL,13,FAt one of their previous networking
OL,14,Fevents, Sophia Nicholls and Kirsten
OL,15,FScott met for the first time.
OL,17,FWithin a few months they'd launched
OL,18,Ftheir own business, which creates
OL,19,Fretreats for people in Dumfries and
OL,20,FGalloway.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
