PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1772745127
OL,3,C'It's ok to be bold': Women encouraged
OL,4,Cto build businesses
OL,6,FSophia Nicholls has this advice for
OL,7,Fother women: "It's ok to be confident.
OL,8,FIt's ok to be bold. I think we need to
OL,9,Fgive permission to women to be
OL,10,Fconfident. I say be bold and come with
OL,11,Fthat energy."
OL,13,FKirsty Adamson, who runs a social
OL,14,Fmedia business, met Kara Hunter who
OL,15,Fowns Kindling Minds through the group
OL,16,Ftoo.
OL,18,FTogether they are working to create
OL,19,Fresources to help other young women
OL,20,Fbecome entrepreneurs.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
