CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1772745127
OL,3,C'It's ok to be bold': Women encouraged
OL,4,Cto build businesses
OL,6,FKara Hunter explains it's "for people
OL,7,Fwho don't actually know what it's like
OL,8,Fto start a business or what it's
OL,9,Factually like to run a business."
OL,11,FBut despite the success of these
OL,12,Fwomen, it's felt there is still a way
OL,13,Fto go for women in business.
OL,15,FJane Morrison-Ross added: "We need to
OL,16,Fmake sure that women have access to
OL,17,Ffunding, to sales training, to the
OL,18,Fnetworks that men have always had.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
