OL,3,C'It's ok to be bold': Women encouraged
OL,4,Cto build businesses
OL,6,F"35 percent of FTSE 350 companies are
OL,7,Fwomen led or have senior women
OL,8,Finvolved, it's not enough yet. We know
OL,9,Fthere's a lack of equaty on how that
OL,10,Fworks, there's a lack of
OL,11,Frepresentative on boards, we have to
OL,12,Fchange all that and make sure women
OL,13,Fare right there at the table."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/6
